def solve():
    (n, m, x, y) = map(int, input().split())
    if (n - 1) % x == 0 and (m - 1) % y == 0 or (n >= 2 and m >= 2 and ((n - 2) % x == 0) and ((m - 2) % y == 0)):
        print('Chefirnemo')
    else:
        print('Pofik')
for _ in range(int(input())):
    solve()
